Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.49,0:24:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,想插進裡面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.99,0:24:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,想要吧 讓我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.26,0:25:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.61,0:25:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒好厲害
